<i>adverb</i>: 쓱쓱 [쓱쓱] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>쓱쓱 [쓱쓱]</dt><br>
<dd>1. rubbing; scrubbing</dd><br>
<dd>자꾸 슬쩍 문지르거나 비비는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the movement of rubbing or scrubbing something lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. with ease; without trouble</dd><br>
<dd>일을 거침없이 손쉽게 해내는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of doing something easily.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>